high_descs: Turn left and go forward to the sink.
Pick up the lettuce from inside of the sink.
Turn around and move forward, and then turn left and go to the fridge.
Open the fridge, put the lettuce inside and chill it, then take the lettuce out.
Turn left and go forward, then turn right to face the sink.
Put the lettuce in the sink.
anns.task_desc: Put cold lettuce in the sink.

high_descs: Take a step forward, then turn left and walk over to the sink.
Pick up the head of lettuce out of the sink.
Turn around and walk forward, then turn left and walk over to the fridge.
Put the head of lettuce in the fridge for a couple seconds to let it get cold then take it out.
Turn left and walk towards the white table, then turn right and walk up to the sink.
Put the chilled head of lettuce in the sink basin.
anns.task_desc: Put a chilled head of lettuce in the sink.

high_descs: Turn left and walk forward to the kitchen sink.
Pick up the head of lettuce that is in the kitchen sink.
Turn around completely, turn left, walk forward a few steps, then turn left to face the refrigerator.
Chill the head of lettuce in the fridge before taking it back out.
Turn the left, walk forward a few steps, then turn to the right to face the kitchen sink.
Place the head of lettuce in the kitchen sink.
anns.task_desc: Place a chilled head of lettuce in the kitchen sink.
